name: Unter Null
description: '''Erica Dunham''', better known by her stage name '''Unter Null''', founded the solo [[aggrotech]] music project in 1998 at the age of 17, while living in [[Seattle]], United States. {{As of|2012}}, she is based in [[Portland, Oregon]]. Dunham is trained in [[Piano|classical piano]], [[cello]] and [[guitar]].
